A dramatically lit, slightly surreal sorcery card illustration depicting a chaotic, joyful scene: a muscular, nude warrior (suggestive of "tits and ass") surrounded by a swirling vortex of beer bottles and hand-drawn creature sketches erupting from the vortex, resembling a drunken, energetic summoning. Style: Old master painting, detailed textures, vibrant colors, emphasis on movement and energy, reminiscent of Gustave Moreau, with a slightly unsettling, dreamlike quality.